		<p>Takashi, you&#8217;re a tool especially if you are one of the  leechers. The people who you claim to &#8216;steal&#8217; from creators actually put their fuckin&#8217; money, time and effort to bring to you for free all the manga that you would have had to pay otherwise and learn the language to read, you big moron. </p>
